Documentation indicates that all we need to do to override udebs from target server is to copy replacement udebs into localdebs and 
copy a new  sources.list.udeb.local file into build directory.

However, the makefile unconditionally rebuilds the sources.list.udeb.local file, preventing the override from working.
Here is the diff, just removing that section so we can always override with local udebs:

688,692d687
< 	else \
< 		gen-sources.list.udeb "$(SYSTEM_SOURCES_LIST)" $(USE_UDEBS_FROM) $(UDEB_COMPONENTS) $(USE_PROPOSED_UPDATES); \
< 		if [ "$(USE_UNRELEASED)" = 1 ]; then \
< 			gen-sources.list.udeb "$(SYSTEM_SOURCES_LIST)" unreleased $(UDEB_COMPONENTS); \
< 		fi \
